{"tid":131312,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［道德撚］鐵路難題","createTime":"2017-02-23T03:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T07:08:19.000Z","uid":17270,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba27e91007b887ad46c15210fafb6ae47a114b1","tid":131312,"uid":17270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"設想你眼前有列失控的電車，以時速六十英里迎面衝來，你卻看到電車不遠的前方分別有五個鐵路工人，以及一個鐵路工人在兩條軌道上專心工作，將來不及逃離險境。<br />\n<br />\n正好在你的面前是可以令電車轉轍軌道的控桿，如果你不操控轉轍軌道，便即有五位工人被撞死，假如你及時轉轍，便有一個工人被撞死；面對這個緊急情況，你將如何抉擇？<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：企定定睇五條友比人車死<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：犧牲一個救五個"},{"pid":"c53a7941471f8182554f705978ca5b61a12a386c","tid":131312,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:57:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dff7475bcef4cfac53c083824773b7e5df52412","tid":131312,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"跳軌自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a80b4edd83dc666f4d4978fba9313643cb4327d","tid":131312,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:59:45.000Z","msg":"緊係即刻飛過去徒手整停部電車LA，咁咪救哂所有人囉~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149e54ed3b4cd60adba9a429cbb10f9af4269283","tid":131312,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-N_RZJUAQY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-N_RZJUAQY4&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d36b2533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-N_RZJUAQY4</a><br />\n自己睇"},{"pid":"730dcd2fde146100a585c635051501fd0750337b","tid":131312,"uid":57357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"呢條好似以前year 1第一堂哲學堂有問過，不過之後就無上了"},{"pid":